Nigerian ladies have taken to Twitter to entertain users after participating in the waist bead challenge. The beautiful women flooded Twitter with their tantalizing waistbead photos. It all started when a Twitter user who is also a Chemical Engineer, Mofeoluwa asked ladies to send in pictures of their waist beads to the platform and even volunteered to share the photos for those who are not bold enough. As seen in the pictures below, the beads come in different colors and sizes and may also include decorative stones, crystals, or charms. According to ancient stories, waist beads stand as an exclusive symbol of feminity. See the photos below: Source